<ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">Giovanni Agnelli -AMP- Co.</ENAMEX> announced a transaction that will strengthen its indirect control of <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">Fiat S.p . A.</ENAMEX> and will admit <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Prince Karim Aga Khan</ENAMEX> as its first non-family shareholder .
