<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">The Aga Khan</ENAMEX> , meanwhile , agreed to trade some of his stake in <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Luxembourg</ENAMEX> - based <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">Ifint S.A.</ENAMEX> , another <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Agnelli</ENAMEX> family company , for <ENAMEX TYPE="PERCENT">7.45 %</ENAMEX> of <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">Giovanni Agnelli -AMP- Co. 's</ENAMEX> capital .
